/* 
# <Mode, Setting, Pump Num, Value>
# Mode can be SETTING, RUN, JOG, STOP
# Setting can be SPEED, ACCEL, DELTA, ONE, FEW, ALL, ZERO
# Pump number can be 1 or 2 or 3 or 12 or 13 or 23. (## indicates two pumps to run)
